[[paragraphs]]
text = "Zombie Game is my idea for a zombie game based on games like DayZ and Project Zomboid. The game was more designed with VR in mind but I am designing ways to make the gameplay available for both as s&box's VR implementation is a bit barebones at the moment."

[[paragraphs]]
text = "The project originally started on Unity but eventually moved to s&box when I got access due to my familiarity with Source over Unity."

